{"tid":834147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨派整合！青政梁頌恆加盟「香港民族陣綫」任發言人","createTime":"2018-09-24T04:09:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-24T04:55:44.000Z","uid":48093,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"564e12902a7ba5805829d3e03baff2dc8f5326df","tid":834147,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:09:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180924/large/1537761806_53c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180924%2Flarge%2F1537761806_53c9.jpg&h=36c92126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港民族黨今日遭政府正式刊憲禁止運作，相關港獨及自決等異見組織或面臨相同命運，青年新政、香港眾志、香港學生獨立聯盟，甚至支聯會都是高危組織。早前曾稱取締事件反映新興團體步上末路的青年新政梁頌恆，近日原來加入另一個提倡獨立的組織「香港民族陣綫」，並擔任發言人一職。<br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫今早在facebook發文宣布，梁頌恆加盟該組織，並擔任發言人一職，指「此舉有利於雙方資源上、行動上、情報上的更高效整合」，相信「泛獨陣營各部的整全與合作，將是繼續推動歷史齒輪前進的先決條件！」<br />\n<br />\n香港民族陣綫在文中指，過去幾年港人被「港共、支共」壓迫，政治權利、言論自由、新聞自由以及法治公正性一併淪陷，又形容「泛獨派抗爭力量日漸散碎」，認為陣營需要壯大團結，互利合作，更自言「作為香港民族的領路人」、「絕無懷憂喪志、自暴自棄的本錢」，呼籲其他人加入。<br />\n翻查資料可見，香港民族陣綫是成立於2015年的本土派組織，提倡港人享有聯合國《公民及政治權利國際公約》所賦予的權利，提出「民族自決」，曾與「學生動源」等到學校外派傳單及設街站，宣揚「香港獨立」。《蘋果》正聯絡梁頌恆了解加入新組織一事。"},{"pid":"42b08d09b6b4622a9818340b2039455b17d508ed","tid":834147,"uid":105678,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:23:37.000Z","msg":"香港獨立！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c7bd1a7cd44e187dc48dd2da809e302eb4ba02","tid":834147,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"民陣?"},{"pid":"eb5532ab24a790d0f1b335eedad7665f6a249174","tid":834147,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67c7bd1a7cd44e187dc48dd2da809e302eb4ba02","tid":834147,"uid":30633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:24:32.000Z","msg":"民陣?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n民間人權陣線只係左膠。"},{"pid":"73cfad7418bbbb4ed050d2913a74438581f43aee","tid":834147,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:32:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.goodsmile.info/cgm/images/product/20180403/7179/51200/large/a8c9c547b4f350b8a6da9ebd27481cb4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.goodsmile.info%2Fcgm%2Fimages%2Fproduct%2F20180403%2F7179%2F51200%2Flarge%2Fa8c9c547b4f350b8a6da9ebd27481cb4.jpg&h=bc0f54da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40fc8acb8446026a3d77174ce250bca32042cb5e","tid":834147,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T04:55:44.000Z","msg":"Support"}]}